# Build artifacts. Each project has its own target/ dir.
/target
**/target
# monocoque's tokio variant builds into a separate target dir.
**/target-tokio

# C++ target build artifacts
targets/libzmq_cpp_target/build/
*.o
*.obj

# Local run scratch (raw telemetry before archival)
/scratch/
*.hgrm
*.profraw

# Rendered run archives. These are regenerated on every run from scratch/ by
# scripts/render_results.py; keep them out of version control so local dev-host
# runs (non-admissible numbers) don't churn the repo. index.json is the manifest
# render rewrites, so it is ignored too.
docs/history/*

# Cargo.lock is intentionally NOT ignored. Every project here is a binary, and
# the arena requires deterministic builds: the orchestrator and each standalone
# target commit their lockfiles so a grid run is reproducible.
